Flow of messages as shown in messages_table.png

A vehicle approaches the crossing zone
Vehicle OBU will broadcast vehicle status
Hazard detection logic determines collision risk
Hazard warning is sent using DSRC
Pedestrian wearable will receive the message
Direction of hazard is identified
Vibrotactile pattern is selected
Actuators in insole provide vibration pattern according to direction
Pedestrian responds to safety cue.

